{"tid":666755,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲格：曾差點簽下C.朗 他本能改寫阿仙奴歷史","createTime":"2018-05-16T06:52:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T09:05:27.000Z","uid":54373,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"adff20f5e218825bc6d4fa4a8edeb0a99076cd4c","tid":666755,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:52:03.000Z","msg":"2018年05月16日12:29<br />\n雲格稱自己差點簽下C.朗拿度美斯<br />\n雲格稱自己差點簽下C.朗拿度美斯<br />\n<br />\n　　《每日鏡報》報導，雲格參加球迷問答時，後悔當年沒有簽下C.朗拿度和美斯。<br />\n<br />\n　　雲格曾簽下了亨利、法比加斯和韋拉等人，這些都是他的經典收購，但他也錯過了不少巨星。<br />\n<br />\n　　<br />\n<br />\n　　在和球迷告別之際，他表示：「我差點簽下C.朗拿度，我認為簽下他會改變阿仙奴球會的歷史。C.朗拿度當年距離我們非常非常近。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「美斯也是，因為我們對他感興趣。法比加斯加盟時，我們也邀請美斯和比基加盟，但沒有成功。」"},{"pid":"8543d1d2fd2279c53f49e7b9658bf29558a9362d","tid":666755,"uid":63588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:53:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> 雲加大燈西</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"08907398422a7f3dfa2b3b160af9a503f89f8c6b","tid":666755,"uid":92603,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:53:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/16/145331_0d5b1c4c7f720f698946c7f6ab08f687.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2F145331_0d5b1c4c7f720f698946c7f6ab08f687.jpg&h=2db8cd96&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0a153c6782e5548a2a16757c8e93e576e3eb2883","tid":666755,"uid":47311,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"08907398422a7f3dfa2b3b160af9a503f89f8c6b","tid":666755,"uid":92603,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:53:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/16/145331_0d5b1c4c7f720f698946c7f6ab08f687.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2F145331_0d5b1c4c7f720f698946c7f6ab08f687.jpg&h=2db8cd96&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:54:42.000Z","msg":"呢堆嚟晒嘅話<br />\n全部去晒做文員長嘆"},{"pid":"3ce7b5d783d1944bc05e7f3e08abcc1725682691","tid":666755,"uid":5843,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:55:42.000Z","msg":"險簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5097b33696f118d15a064406099be8d7a1fc068b","tid":666755,"uid":1984,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:57:50.000Z","msg":"比你簽到肯定無而家呢個level<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c26ea3f384feda1de4667a763cc6a49308d7310","tid":666755,"uid":173397,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:59:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0922fadf6890077f0d756f030f82a53f6fa932ae","tid":666755,"uid":1977,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"08907398422a7f3dfa2b3b160af9a503f89f8c6b","tid":666755,"uid":92603,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:53:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/16/145331_0d5b1c4c7f720f698946c7f6ab08f687.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2F145331_0d5b1c4c7f720f698946c7f6ab08f687.jpg&h=2db8cd96&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:59:54.000Z","msg":"個龍廢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bce3f698611549add6bf7627f80d0ad7854d73f","tid":666755,"uid":92603,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T07:00:52.000Z","msg":"前鋒：蘇亞雷斯<br />\n<br />\n就是那件4000萬1鎊事件。蘇亞雷斯效力利物浦時，合約中有一項4000萬鎊的違約金，而阿仙奴就開出4000萬1鎊，竟被利物浦回絕！時任利物浦謝拉特表示，就算利物浦接受報道，蘇亞雷斯都不會走，因為謝拉特已經說服到蘇亞雷斯多留一年。謝拉特在2014年說：「去年夏天，他受到球會的處罰，被迫單獨操練，我就跟他談過。我跟他說，別去阿仙奴了。我很尊重阿仙奴，但對他們來說，蘇亞雷斯太過優秀了。我說如果你為利物浦攻入30個球，贏得英格蘭雙料足球先生，他們（皇馬及巴塞）就會主動來找你。」最後，蘇亞雷斯選擇了巴塞及「雲格險簽隊」。<br />\n<br />\n中場：加里夫巴利<br />\n<br />\n雲格表示，錯失了加里夫巴利，令他投效「雲格險簽隊」，是他教練生涯一大失誤。他表示，當他由修咸頓收購禾確特時，已經留意得到禾確特的青年軍隊友巴利，但因為判斷出錯，所以沒有出手。雲格在2013年說：「當時我有艾殊利高爾及基歷治，所以不需要再多一位左閘，但我犯了一大錯誤，原來巴利可以踢中場。巴利起初在熱刺踢得不好，但踢中場就非常好。有時一個球員能否成功，很視乎他是否踢一個正確位置。」"},{"pid":"f8416d3fbda6ce5222d357e10ceb1bb19872bcc8","tid":666755,"uid":21028,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0922fadf6890077f0d756f030f82a53f6fa932ae","tid":666755,"uid":1977,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"08907398422a7f3dfa2b3b160af9a503f89f8c6b","tid":666755,"uid":92603,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:53:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/16/145331_0d5b1c4c7f720f698946c7f6ab08f687.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2F145331_0d5b1c4c7f720f698946c7f6ab08f687.jpg&h=2db8cd96&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:59:54.000Z","msg":"個龍廢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T07:01:30.000Z","msg":"成隊野 攻力勁到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除咗中間個黑人就算啦"},{"pid":"39ab8a3b8e041ca585c349c7c60be0293a1429c7","tid":666755,"uid":36497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T07:01:57.000Z","msg":"雲加已經改變左阿記歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c763a48073eeb9aeb5f6135419ac2be7d0fc8ee6","tid":666755,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T07:02:57.000Z","msg":"「我差點簽下C.朗拿度，我認為簽下他會改變C.朗拿度的歷史。C.朗拿度當年距離我們非常非常近。」"},{"pid":"acc1fccbefca7f2d71e543d512d561ddd164c469","tid":666755,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8416d3fbda6ce5222d357e10ceb1bb19872bcc8","tid":666755,"uid":21028,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0922fadf6890077f0d756f030f82a53f6fa932ae","tid":666755,"uid":1977,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0